Truths<~>of<~>the<~>physical<~>order<~>may<~>possess<~>much<~>external<~>significance<~>,<~>*NL*<~>but<~>internal<~>significance<~>they<~>have<~>none<~>.<~>The<~>latter<~>is<~>the<~>privilege<~>*NL*<~>of<~>intellectual<~>and<~>moral<~>truths<~>,<~>which<~>are<~>concerned<~>with<~>the<~>*NL*<~>objectivation<~>of<~>the<~>will<~>in<~>its<~>highest<~>stages<~>,<~>whereas<~>physical<~>*NL*<~>truths<~>are<~>concerned<~>with<~>it<~>in<~>its<~>lowest<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>For<~>example<~>,<~>if<~>we<~>could<~>establish<~>the<~>truth<~>of<~>what<~>up<~>till<~>now<~>is<~>*NL*<~>only<~>a<~>conjecture<~>,<~>namely<~>,<~>that<~>it<~>is<~>the<~>action<~>of<~>the<~>sun<~>which<~>*NL*<~>produces<~>thermoelectricity<~>at<~>the<~>equator<~>;<~>that<~>this<~>produces<~>*NL*<~>terrestrial<~>magnetism<~>;<~>and<~>that<~>this<~>magnetism<~>,<~>again<~>,<~>is<~>the<~>cause<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>_<~>aurora<~>borealis<~>_<~>,<~>these<~>would<~>be<~>truths<~>externally<~>of<~>great<~>,<~>but<~>*NL*<~>internally<~>of<~>little<~>,<~>significance<~>.<~>On<~>the<~>other<~>hand<~>,<~>examples<~>*NL*<~>of<~>internal<~>significance<~>are<~>furnished<~>by<~>all<~>great<~>and<~>true<~>*NL*<~>philosophical<~>systems<~>;<~>by<~>the<~>catastrophe<~>of<~>every<~>good<~>tragedy<~>;<~>nay<~>,<~>*NL*<~>even<~>by<~>the<~>observation<~>of<~>human<~>conduct<~>in<~>the<~>extreme<~>manifestations<~>*NL*<~>of<~>its<~>morality<~>and<~>immorality<~>,<~>of<~>its<~>good<~>and<~>its<~>evil<~>character<~>.<~>*NL*<~>For<~>all<~>these<~>are<~>expressions<~>of<~>that<~>reality<~>which<~>takes<~>outward<~>*NL*<~>shape<~>as<~>the<~>world<~>,<~>and<~>which<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>highest<~>stages<~>of<~>its<~>*NL*<~>objectivation<~>,<~>proclaims<~>its<~>innermost<~>nature<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>To<~>say<~>that<~>the<~>world<~>has<~>only<~>a<~>physical<~>and<~>not<~>a<~>moral<~>significance<~>*NL*<~>is<~>the<~>greatest<~>and<~>most<~>pernicious<~>of<~>all<~>errors<~>,<~>the<~>fundamental<~>*NL*<~>blunder<~>,<~>the<~>real<~>perversity<~>of<